Package: oeis.tools
Title: OEIS Toolkit for R
Version: 0.2.1
Author: Enrique Pérez Herrero [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Enrique Pérez Herrero <energycode.org@gmail.com>
Description: Focused R toolkit for working with OEIS integer sequences: 
    fetch metadata, parse b-files, and plot sequence values quickly.
    Provides an object-oriented interface to the Online 
    Encyclopedia of Integer Sequences (OEIS) at <https://oeis.org>.
